children.text: Enough Said spoken word series event held at Bistro 4 (4040 St. Laurent, Montreal, QC, H2W 1Y8, Canada) on January 30, 1995, hosted by Lee Gotham. Feature performances by Victoria Stanton and Ian Stephens. Supporting/open mic performances by Matthew Legault, Shaughnessy Bishop-Stall, Thoth Harris, Steve Godin, Justin McGrail, and more.
